    "body": "### Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\nI noticed a change of behavior of the following scenario between spack@v0.12.1 and spack@develop :\r\n \r\n```console\r\n$ module load gcc/8.1.0\r\n$ spack compiler find\r\n```\r\n\r\n### The problem\r\n\r\nOn \"release\" tag v0.12.1, the compiler is found, on the develop branch, it isn\u2019t.\r\n\r\n### System information \r\n\r\nThe issue occurs on a supercomputer using lmod mechanism for modules.\r\n\r\n",
